這場分站是[[法拉利車隊|法拉利車隊]]參加的第900場大獎賽。<ref name=ferrari>{{cite web | title = Belgian GP - Off again at a classic circuit | url = http://formula1.ferrari.com/en/belgian-grand-prix-off-again-at-a-classic-circuit/?utm_source=Affiliation-ES&utm_medium=Tradedoubler-ES&utm_content=ES&utm_campaign=Feed | publisher = Scuderia Ferrari | accessdate = 2015-08-23 | language = en | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150824014843/http://formula1.ferrari.com/en/belgian-grand-prix-off-again-at-a-classic-circuit/?utm_source=Affiliation-ES&utm_medium=Tradedoubler-ES&utm_content=ES&utm_campaign=Feed | archivedate = 2015-08-24 | deadurl = no }}</ref>在[[斯帕-弗朗科爾尚賽道|斯帕]]有著名成就的現役車手[[奇米·雷克南|奇米·雷克南]]為法拉利駕車介紹賽道，<ref name=ferrari />他也在比賽一週前與該隊延長一年合約。<ref>{{cite web | title = Kimi Raikkonen handed contract extension by Ferrari for 2016 | url = http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/aug/19/kimi-raikkonen-handed-contract-extension-ferrari-f1-2016 | publisher = The Guardian | accessdate = 2015-08-23 | date = 2015-08-19 | language = en | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150824015759/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/aug/19/kimi-raikkonen-handed-contract-extension-ferrari-f1-2016 | archivedate = 2015-08-24 | deadurl = no }}</ref>[[梅賽德斯車隊|梅賽德斯]]為斯帕賽道引進新的低下壓力後尾翼，並有著類似{{F1|2006}}{{Le|麥拉倫MP4-21|McLaren MP4-21}}的勺子形設計。<ref>{{cite web |title=Mercedes F1 W06 Hybrid - Spa-Francorchamps rear wing |url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/technical/2015/8/mercedes-f1-w06-hybrid---spa-francorchamps-rear-wing.html |publisher=FIA |accessdate=2015-08-24 |date=2015-08-23 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825081140/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/technical/2015/8/mercedes-f1-w06-hybrid---spa-francorchamps-rear-wing.html |archivedate=2015-08-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Tech: Mercedes' twisted wing explained |url=http://plus.autosport.com/premium/feature/6648/tech-mercedes-twisted-wing-explained/ |website=autosport.com |accessdate=2015-08-24 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825081235/http://plus.autosport.com/premium/feature/6648/tech-mercedes-twisted-wing-explained/ |archivedate=2015-08-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>其目的在於找到在斯帕賽道長直道上的低下壓力，以及在賽道較多彎角的第二區段中能保有足夠的抓地力，兩者之間的平衡點。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Somerfield|first1=Matt|title=Tech Corner: Mercedes Spa Updates|url=http://planetf1.com/driver/3260/73319/Tech-Corner-Mercedes-Spa-Updates|website=planetf1.com|accessdate=2015-08-26|date=2015-08-25|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150826161339/http://planetf1.com/driver/3260/73319/Tech-Corner-Mercedes-Spa-Updates|archivedate=2015-08-26|deadurl=yes}}</ref>另外，[[紅牛車隊|紅牛]]在週五自由練習賽期間，測試了兩種不同的尾翼。其中，[[丹尼爾·里卡多|丹尼爾·里卡多]]用上極低下壓力的，[[丹尼爾·科維亞特|丹尼爾·科維亞特]]則測試「斯帕專用設置版本」尾翼，這套尾翼也是兩位車手最終在排位賽及正賽中所使用的，能夠減緩輪胎劣化。<ref>{{cite web|title=Red Bull RB11 - rear wing updates|url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/technical/2015/8/red-bull-rb11---rear-wing-updates.html|publisher=FIA|accessdate=2015-08-26|date=2015-08-26|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150826161917/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/technical/2015/8/red-bull-rb11---rear-wing-updates.html|archivedate=2015-08-26|deadurl=no}}</ref>[[麥拉倫車隊|麥拉倫]]換上了新的動力單元，旨在藉由導入的修改來達到與法拉利動力單元相等的水平。<ref>{{cite web|last1 = Anderson|first1 = Ben|title = Honda aiming to match Ferrari with Formula 1 power unit update|url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120337|website = autosport.com|accessdate = 2015-08-25|date = 2015-08-17|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150825132850/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120337|archivedate = 2015-08-25|deadurl = no}}</ref>然而，麥拉論賽車指導[[埃里克·布里耶|埃里克·布里耶]]則提醒說，這套單元要等到[[2015年新加坡大獎賽|新加坡分站]]才會有顯著的獲益，他也預期這會是一場「艱難的」比利時大獎賽。<ref>{{cite web|last1 = Galloway|first1 = James|title = McLaren-Honda expect 'difficult' Belgian GP despite new-spec engine|url = http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12479/9954624/mclaren-honda-expect-difficult-belgian-gp-despite-new-spec-engine|publisher = Sky Sports|accessdate = 2015-08-25|date = 2015-08-18|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150820013700/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12479/9954624/mclaren-honda-expect-difficult-belgian-gp-despite-new-spec-engine|archivedate = 2015-08-20|deadurl = no}}</ref>為了配合全新的動力單元，該隊推出新的引擎蓋。[[麥拉倫MP4-30|麥拉倫MP4-30]]額外的更新還包括前底盤「史無前例」的托盤設計，以及較低的側箱和全新位置的散熱器，以冷卻電子回收系統。<ref>{{cite web|title=McLaren MP4-30 - slotted tea tray|url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/technical/2015/8/mclaren-mp4-30---slotted-tea-tray.html|publisher=FIA|accessdate=2015-08-26|date=2015-08-24|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150826162220/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/technical/2015/8/mclaren-mp4-30---slotted-tea-tray.html|archivedate=2015-08-26|deadurl=no}}</ref>

[[路易斯·漢米爾頓|路易斯·漢米爾頓]]在車手積分榜上以202分領先，位居第2的[[尼可·羅斯堡|尼可·羅斯堡]]落後21分。在[[2015年匈牙利大獎賽|前一分站]]奪冠的法拉利車手[[賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾|賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾]]縮小了差距，與羅斯堡相差21分。<ref>{{cite web|title = 2015 Driver Standings|url = http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/results/2015-driver-standings.html|publisher = FIA|accessdate = 2015-08-25|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150820232517/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/results/2015-driver-standings.html|archivedate = 2015-08-20|language = en|deadurl = no}}</ref>在車隊積分榜方面，梅賽德斯以383分領先147分的法拉利，第3的[[威廉斯車隊|威廉斯]]則再落後85分。<ref>{{cite web|title = 2015 Constructor Standings|url = http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/results/2015-constructor-standings.html|publisher = FIA|accessdate = 2015-08-25|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150820232535/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/results/2015-constructor-standings.html|archivedate = 2015-08-20|language = en|deadurl = no}}</ref>

==== 規則變更 ====
為了限制維修站車隊監控區在起跑時對車手的影響力，自比利時大獎賽後，官方制訂了新的起跑程序規則。一旦車手離開維修站前往發車位，便僅能再調整其中一個離合器撥片。<ref name=startmclaren>{{Cite web | url = http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/features/2015/8/pre-spa-analysis-mclaren-the-big-winners-of-start-changes.html | title = Pre-Spa analysis - McLaren the big winners of start changes? | publisher = [[FIA|FIA]] | date = 2015-08-21 | accessdate = 2015-08-21 | website = formula1.com | language = en | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150822142144/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/features/2015/8/pre-spa-analysis-mclaren-the-big-winners-of-start-changes.html | archivedate = 2015-08-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>車手們對此的看法不一，尼可·羅斯堡稱這項新的起跑程序會讓比賽更具挑戰性，<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120012 | title = New Formula 1 grand prix start rules 'a big change' - Nico Rosberg | website = autosport.com | date = 2015-07-17 | accessdate = 2015-08-21 | first = Ben | last = Anderson | language = en | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150725112713/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120012 | archivedate = 2015-07-25 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>[[費爾南多·阿隆索|費爾南多·阿隆索]]認為這並非重大的改變，<ref name=startmclaren />而丹尼爾·里卡多則希望這項新的程序能夠幫助他的車隊。<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/interviews/2015/8/exclusive-daniel-ricciardo-q-a--start-changes-could-help-red-bul.html | title = Exclusive Daniel Ricciardo Q&A: Start changes could help Red Bull | publisher = [[FIA|FIA]] | date = 2015-08-20 | accessdate = 2015-08-21 | website = formula1.com | language = en | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150820232851/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/interviews/2015/8/exclusive-daniel-ricciardo-q-a--start-changes-could-help-red-bul.html | archivedate = 2015-08-20 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

