[[路特斯車隊|路特斯車隊]]在斯帕週末面臨一起官司，前測試車手[[查爾斯·皮克|查爾斯·皮克]]認為車隊違背了協議，未提供他足夠的時間駕駛該隊的{{le|蓮花E22|Lotus E22|2014年車輛}}。隨著這起官司進入仲裁程序，蓮花在這場分站後，可能將面臨車輛被扣押且不能任意移動的風險。<ref>{{cite web | last1 = Rencken | first1 = Dieter | last2 = Parkes | first2 = Ian | title = Lotus facing threat of F1 cars being impounded following Belgian GP | url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120397 | website = autosport.com | accessdate = 2015-08-22 | date = 2015-08-21 | language = en | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150822064745/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120397 | archivedate = 2015-08-22 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>

=== 自由練習賽 ===
根據[[2015年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2015年賽季]]的規則，比賽周末將舉行三階段自由練習賽，週五的兩場長一個半小時，剩餘的一場一小時練習賽則位在週六排位賽之前。<ref name="pracreg3">{{cite web |title=Practice and qualifying |url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/inside-f1/rules-regs/Practice_qualifying_and_race_start_procedure.html |publisher=FIA |accessdate=2015-06-21 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702230312/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/inside-f1/rules-regs/Practice_qualifying_and_race_start_procedure.html |archivedate=2015-07-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>在週五上午的第一階段練習賽，尼可·羅斯堡最初遭遇動力單元故障問題，但仍舊成為第一階段的最快車手，領先他的隊友路易斯·漢米爾頓約0.25秒。紅牛的丹尼爾·里卡多位居第3，僅僅比第2的漢米爾頓慢上約0.05秒，第四的奇米·雷克南則再落後里卡多約1秒。此階段經過五十分鐘後，[[帕斯托·馬爾多納多|帕斯托·馬爾多納多]]在經過科姆貝斯（{{Lang|fr|Les Combes}}）彎時，他的{{Le|蓮花E23 Hybrid|Lotus E23 Hybrid}}尾端失去牽引力撞上了輪胎護牆，造成他的車輛右前方損毀並引發了紅旗。<ref name=fp1>{{Cite web | url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120388 | title = Belgian GP: Nico Rosberg leads Lewis Hamilton in first Spa practice | website = autosport.com | date = 2015-08-21 | accessdate = 2015-08-21 | first = James | last = Roberts | language = en | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150824072846/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120388 | archivedate = 2015-08-24 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>為了修復護牆，此階段練習賽中斷了十分鐘。馬爾多納多談到他的事故，表示：「真的非常不走運，因為我差點就能保住車輛了。但是無論如何，事情已經發生。這一直是一條非常困難的賽道，特別在第二區段相較狹窄，當你一有閃失便會出事。但是，這已經發生了，現在我們也無從改變。我們只能持續前進奮鬥了。」<ref>{{cite web | last1 = Barretto | first1 = Lawrence | last2 = Parkes | first2 = Ian | title = Belgian GP: Pastor Maldonado says F1 practice crash 'very unlucky' | url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120401 | website = autosport.com | accessdate = 2015-08-22 | date = 2015-08-21 | language = en | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150824073308/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120401 | archivedate = 2015-08-24 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>蓮花的[[喬里昂·帕爾默|喬里昂·帕爾默]]再次代替[[羅曼·格羅斯讓|羅曼·格羅斯讓]]上場，以第17名完賽。<ref name=fp1 /><ref>{{cite web|last1 = Andrew|first1 = Benson|title = Jolyon Palmer gets Lotus practice role for remaining European races|url = http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/33097912|publisher = BBC|accessdate = 2015-08-25|date = 2015-06-11|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150620214735/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/33097912|archivedate = 2015-06-20|deadurl = no}}</ref>

{{Quote box
 |quote  = 「我沒撞上牆只是運氣好，而非是我的本領……事發的第一刻相當令人震驚，因為這並不是我所能預期到的。突然間，你就在360公里每小時的速度下失去控制，這個感覺非常不好。」
 |source = [[尼可·羅斯堡|尼可·羅斯堡]]，談到他在第二階段自由練習賽發生的打轉。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Collantine |first1=Keith |title='Just lucky' I didn't hit the wall – Rosberg |url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/21/just-lucky-i-didnt-hit-the-wall-rosberg/ |publisher=F1Fanatic |accessdate=2015-08-22 |date=2015-08-21 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825074224/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/21/just-lucky-i-didnt-hit-the-wall-rosberg/ |archivedate=2015-08-25 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>
 |width  = 30%
 |align  = right
}}週五下午的第二階段練習賽又再發生一起事故，尼可·羅斯堡的梅賽德斯後輪爆胎，使得他在布蘭奇蒙特（{{Lang|fr|Blanchimont}}）彎上發生打滑。德國人順利地避開輪胎牆，但此階段仍然出示紅旗，以拖離羅斯堡留在賽道上的車輛。在這起事故之前，羅斯堡便以1分49.687秒的成績寫下此階段的最快圈速，較位居第2的隊友快上約0.3秒。里卡多再度名列第3，落後漢米爾頓約0.4秒，在他之後的是他的紅牛隊友丹尼爾·科維亞特，與羅斯堡相距1秒。威廉斯的[[維爾特利·鮑達斯|維爾特利·鮑達斯]]及[[費利佩·馬薩|費利佩·馬薩]]分別名列第14及第16位，領先兩輛麥拉倫，而兩位[[馬諾車隊|馬諾瑪魯西亞]]則位居最後。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120393 |title=Belgian GP: Mercedes' Nico Rosberg tops practice before tyre blows |website=autosport.com |date=2015-08-21 |accessdate=2015-08-21 |first=Lawrence |last=Barretto |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150822064417/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120393 |archivedate=2015-08-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>隨後，倍耐力認為羅斯堡的爆胎起因於「外力侵擾」，排除了「任何結構完整性問題」的可能性。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Parkes |first1=Ian |title=Belgian GP: 'External cut' caused Nico Rosberg tyre blow - Pirelli |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120410 |website=autosport.com |accessdate=2015-08-22 |date=2015-08-22 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825082537/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120410 |archivedate=2015-08-25 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>不過，這位梅賽德斯車手仍然擔憂輪胎在週日正賽時的穩定性，說道：「問題在於我們並不清楚這一切。是有些推測，但都沒有足夠的證據，所以可以肯定的是這件事仍然令人憂心。」<ref name="tyre">{{cite web|last1 = Barretto|first1 = Lawrence|last2 = Beer|first2 = Matt|title = Belgian F1 GP: Nico Rosberg not reassured over tyres after blowout|url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120420|website = autosport.com|accessdate = 2015-08-22|date = 2015-08-25|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150825134551/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120420|archivedate = 2015-08-25|deadurl = yes}}</ref>

世界冠軍路易斯·漢米爾頓在週六上午的第三階段練習賽重新振作，寫下全場最快圈速，較第2的羅斯堡快上約半秒。經過此階段平淡無奇的練習賽，兩位法拉利車手維泰爾與雷克南則分別位居第3及第4。[[印度威力車隊|印度威力]]的[[塞吉歐·培瑞茲|塞吉歐·培瑞茲]]及[[尼克·胡肯伯格|尼克·胡肯伯格]]則排在了兩位紅牛車手前後，分別取得第5與第8的成績。第三階段唯一出現的事件發生在羅曼·格羅斯讓於16號彎要超越奇米·雷克南時，格羅斯讓被法拉利逼到差點發生打轉，隨後，他向車隊表示雷克南的行為「非常、非常地危險」。<ref>{{cite web|last1 = Collantine|first1 = Keith|title = Hamilton to the fore in final practice|url = http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/22/hamilton-to-the-fore-in-final-practice/|publisher = F1Fanatic|accessdate = 2015-08-22|date = 2015-08-22|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150825140326/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/22/hamilton-to-the-fore-in-final-practice/|archivedate = 2015-08-25|deadurl = yes}}</ref>

=== 排位賽 ===
排位賽共包含三個部分，各個階段分別長18、15、12分鐘，前兩階段各淘汰五名車手。<ref name="pracreg3"/>[[維爾特利·鮑達斯|維爾特利·鮑達斯]]是第一階段（Q1）首位及最後一位出場的車手，在第一階段尾聲上場的一圈使他脫離淘汰名單。首批被淘汰的包括兩位馬諾瑪魯西亞、兩位麥拉倫車手及[[薩伯車隊|薩伯]]的[[費利佩·納斯爾|費利佩·納斯爾]]。儘管[[馬克斯·維斯塔潘|馬克斯·維斯塔潘]]抱怨他的車輛失去動力，但仍順利挺進第二階段。<ref name="f1fanqual2">{{cite web|last1 = Collantine|first1 = Keith|title = Hamilton storms to pole as Ferrari falter at Spa|url = http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/22/hamilton-storms-to-pole-as-ferrari-falter-at-spa/|publisher = F1Fanatic|accessdate = 2015-08-22|date = 2015-08-22|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150825142044/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/22/hamilton-storms-to-pole-as-ferrari-falter-at-spa/|archivedate = 2015-08-25|deadurl = yes}}</ref>

第二階段排位賽，奇米·雷克南因為失去油壓而停在了賽道上。此階段排位賽為了清空賽道出現了短暫的紅旗，等到排位賽恢復後，兩位梅賽德斯車手決定不再上場，因為他們首圈時間已經足夠進入第三階段。馬克斯·維斯塔潘因為車輛故障未能跑完第二階段，使他暫時取得第14位（罰退未計），雷克南則將以第15位發車。<ref>{{cite web|last1 = Rose|first1 = Gary|title = How Belgian GP qualifying unfolded|url = http://www.bbc.com/sport/live/formula1/32542939|publisher = BBC|accessdate = 2015-08-22|date = 2015-08-22|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150825143503/http://www.bbc.com/sport/live/formula1/32542939|archivedate = 2015-08-25|deadurl = no}}</ref>剩餘三位被淘汰的車手為[[马库斯·埃里克松_(赛车运动员)|马库斯·埃里克松]]、丹尼爾·科維亞特及尼克·胡肯伯格。胡肯伯格的時間僅比第10的維泰爾慢上約0.3秒，且他成為唯一無法爭奪桿位的駕駛梅賽德斯動力車輛的車手。<ref name="f1fanqual2"/>
[[File:Hamilton_pole_Belgium_2015.jpg|thumb]]慶祝奪得桿位。]]
路易斯·漢米爾頓是第三階段首位出場作時間的梅賽德斯車手，以約半秒之差刷新了隊友羅斯堡在第二階段的時間。同時，羅斯堡也刷新了他自己的圈時，不過最終仍落後隊友0.458秒，將以第2位發車。這是路易斯·漢米爾頓在本季目前11場分站中，奪得的第10座桿位，這也意味著他提前保住了國際汽聯桿位獎（{{Lang|en|FIA Pole Position Trophy}}）。<ref name="qual2">{{cite web|last1 = Anderson|first1 = Ben|title = Belgian F1 GP: Mercedes' Lewis Hamilton extends pole streak at Spa|url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120418|website = autosport.com|accessdate = 2015-08-22|date = 2015-08-22|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150822143457/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120418|archivedate = 2015-08-22|deadurl = no}}</ref>排在第3位的是威廉斯車手維爾特利·鮑達斯，他以1.3秒之差落後1分47.197秒的漢米爾頓。羅曼·格羅斯讓以[[BBC|BBC]]稱作「極其令人印象深刻」的一圈，排上第4位。塞吉歐·培瑞茲同樣也有不錯的成績，為印度威力拿下第5位。另外，[[2015年匈牙利大獎賽|前一站]]分站冠軍賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾在最後的減速彎發生失誤，僅能排在第9位發車。<ref name="bbcqual">{{cite web|last1 = Benson|first1 = Andrew|title = Lewis Hamilton on Belgian GP pole ahead of Nico Rosberg|url = http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34028115|publisher = BBC|accessdate = 2015-08-22|date = 2015-08-22|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150826032501/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34028115|archivedate = 2015-08-26|deadurl = no}}</ref>

排位賽後，漢米爾頓表示他能有如此的成績，主要是因為他在賽道中段有所改善，說道：「第二區段很有可能是以往我的弱點。從前，我了解路線，但卻無法掌握過彎時機。可以肯定的是，我在最後的這兩圈非常、非常地強勢。」<ref name="tyre2">{{cite web|last1 = Barretto|first1 = Lawrence|last2 = Beer|first2 = Matt|title = Belgian F1 GP: Nico Rosberg not reassured over tyres after blowout|url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120420|website = autosport.com|accessdate = 2015-08-22|date = 2015-08-22|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150825134551/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120420|archivedate = 2015-08-25|deadurl = yes}}</ref>事實上，他在領先羅斯堡的時間大多都落在這個包含賽道大部分彎角的區段。<ref name="bbcqual2">{{cite web|last1 = Benson|first1 = Andrew|title = Lewis Hamilton on Belgian GP pole ahead of Nico Rosberg|url = http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34028115|publisher = BBC|accessdate = 2015-08-22|date = 2015-08-22|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150826032526/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34028115|archivedate = 2015-08-26|deadurl = no}}</ref>他成為繼[[麥可·舒馬克|麥可·舒馬克]]（於[[2000年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2000年]]至{{F1|2001}}達成這項成就<ref name="bbcqual2" />）後，首位連續奪得六座桿位的車手，而上一位在單一賽季取得連續六座桿位的車手是{{F1|1999}}的[[米卡·海基寧|米卡·海基寧]]。<ref name="qual2"/>[[簡森·巴頓|簡森·巴頓]]在取得不理想的排位及接受罰退後，預期這對麥拉倫來說將會是一場「孤獨的比賽」，說道：「事實上，我很享受賽車，當你衝過終點線時，看到自己的時間覺得『還不算糟』。但是，一旦你看到自己與前方車手相差1秒如此大的差距後，真的很心痛。」<ref>{{cite web|last1 = Parkes|first1 = Ian|title = Belgian F1 GP: McLaren's Button and Alonso resigned to lonely race|url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120421|website = autosport.com|accessdate = 2015-08-22|date = 2015-08-22|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150826072154/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120421|archivedate = 2015-08-26|deadurl = no}}</ref>

=== 罰則 ===
[[File:Jenson_Button_Belgium_2015.jpg|thumb]]在取得不理想的排位及罰退後，預期這將會是一場「孤獨的比賽」。]]
麥拉倫原先期盼能從起跑程序改變中得利，<ref name="startmclaren2">{{Cite web|url = http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/features/2015/8/pre-spa-analysis-mclaren-the-big-winners-of-start-changes.html|title = Pre-Spa analysis – McLaren the big winners of start changes?|publisher = FIA|date = 2015-08-21|accessdate = 2015-08-21|website = formula1.com|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150822142144/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/features/2015/8/pre-spa-analysis-mclaren-the-big-winners-of-start-changes.html|archivedate = 2015-08-22|deadurl = no}}</ref>不過本站將從最後兩位發車。他們於[[2015年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2015年賽季]]已經超出使用一具動力單元配額後，又在[[2015年匈牙利大獎賽|匈牙利大獎賽]]換上第六具動力單元，<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120063|title = McLaren F1's Alonso and Button get 'free' new Hondas for Hungary|website = autosport.com|date = 2015-07-23|accessdate = 2015-08-21|first = Lawrence|last = Barretto|deadurl = yes|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150801042023/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120063|archivedate = 2015-08-01}}</ref>接著，於週五的比利時再為兩輛車都換上第七具重大修正版的動力單元。隨後，由於季中的規則修訂，麥拉倫又在週六更換另一具動力單元，<ref>{{cite web|last1 = Parkes|first1 = Ian|title = Belgian F1 GP: McLaren's Button and Alonso have second Honda change|url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120413|website = autosport.com|accessdate = 2015-08-22|date = 2015-08-22|deadurl = yes|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150826124811/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120413|archivedate = 2015-08-26}}</ref>意味著他們所需接受的罰則將不再是賽中加時，且在剩餘的賽季，該隊將有兩具動力單元的額度不用擔心會有額外的後果。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/8/mclaren-set-to-start-at-rear-of-spa-grid.html|title = McLaren set to start at rear of Spa grid|publisher = FIA|date = 2015-08-21|accessdate = 2015-08-21|website = formula1.com|deadurl = no|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150822113402/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/8/mclaren-set-to-start-at-rear-of-spa-grid.html|archivedate = 2015-08-22}}</ref><ref name="McLarenPowerUnits">{{Cite web|url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120385|title = McLaren to make double engine changes on both F1 cars at Spa|website = autosport.com|date = 2015-08-20|accessdate = 2015-08-21|first = Lawrence|last = Barretto|deadurl = yes|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150820231645/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120385|archivedate = 2015-08-20}}</ref>兩位車手在這場比賽總計要被罰退105位，刷新了新的一級方程式賽車紀錄。<ref>{{cite news|url = http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34008319|title = Belgian Grand Prix: McLaren given 105-place grid penalty|first = Andrew|last = Benson|work = [[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|publisher = [[BBC|BBC]]|date = 2015-08-22|accessdate = 2015-08-22|deadurl = no|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150826125855/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34008319|archivedate = 2015-08-26}}</ref>

馬克斯·維斯塔潘在週五換上他的第六具動力單元後，須接受10位罰退。<ref name="KvyatPenalty">{{cite web|last1 = Collantine|first1 = Keith|title = Verstappen set for engine penalty, Kvyat reprimanded|url = http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/21/verstappen-set-for-engine-penalty-kvyat-reprimanded/|publisher = F1Fanatic|accessdate = 2015-08-22|date = 2015-08-21|deadurl = yes|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150825070612/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/21/verstappen-set-for-engine-penalty-kvyat-reprimanded/|archivedate = 2015-08-25}}</ref>蓮花在週六更換羅曼·格羅斯讓的變速箱後，法國人被判罰退5位，使得他的第4發車位後退至第9位。<ref name="GrosjeanPenalty">{{cite web|last1 = Barretto|first1 = Lawrence|title = Belgian F1 GP: Romain Grosjean handed penalty for gearbox change|url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120417|website = autosport.com|accessdate = 2015-08-22|date = 2015-08-22|deadurl = yes|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150823160315/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120417|archivedate = 2015-08-23}}</ref>基於同樣的原因，奇米·雷克南也接受了5位罰退，再加上其他車手的罰則，讓他原先的排位下滑2名。<ref name="KimiPenalty">{{cite web|last1 = Parkes|first1 = Ian|title = Belgian GP F1: Ferrari's Kimi Raikkonen gets gearbox penalty|url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120440|website = autosport.com|accessdate = 2015-08-23|date = 2015-08-23|deadurl = yes|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150823160409/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120440|archivedate = 2015-08-23}}</ref>

=== 正賽 ===
起跑前，尼克·胡肯伯格在回報他的印度威力失去動力後，回到了車庫，不過最終仍返回發車格。他在暖胎圈時再度遭遇相同問題，加上他的車輛在發車格上熄火，使得起跑程序被迫中斷，須再執行一次暖胎圈。<ref name="bbcrace">{{cite web|last1 = Rose|first1 = Gary|title = How the Belgian GP unfolded|url = http://www.bbc.com/sport/live/formula1/32542940|publisher = BBC|accessdate = 2015-08-23|date = 2015-08-23|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150823132454/http://www.bbc.com/sport/live/formula1/32542940|archivedate = 2015-08-23|deadurl = no}}</ref>[[小卡洛斯·塞恩斯|小卡洛斯·塞恩斯]]在第二次暖胎圈也出現類似狀況，隨後被車隊叫回維修站。最後，他在比賽起跑後出場。<ref name="guardrace">{{cite web|last1 = McVeigh|first1 = Niall|title = F1: Lewis Hamilton wins the Belgian Grand Prix 2015 – as it happened|url = http://www.theguardian.com/sport/live/2015/aug/23/f1-belgian-grand-prix-live-2015|publisher = The Guardian|accessdate = 2015-08-23|date = 2015-08-23|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150824103313/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/live/2015/aug/23/f1-belgian-grand-prix-live-2015|archivedate = 2015-08-24|deadurl = no}}</ref>因此，比賽距離縮短至43圈。<ref name="bbcrace" />
[[File:Hülkenberg_Belgium_2015.jpg|thumb]]未能順利起跑。]]
正賽展開，尼可·羅斯堡的起步並不順利，被後方的培瑞茲、里卡多及鮑達斯超越，暫居第5名，不過他在首圈最後一彎順利超車來到第4名。麥拉倫的費爾南多·阿隆索起跑則是相當成功，名次上升至第12名。路易斯·漢米爾頓保持著他的領先地位，很早便與第2名的培瑞茲拉開差距。第2圈，賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾藉著鮑達斯的鎖死，順利在1號彎超車，來到第5名緊追前方的羅斯堡。帕斯托·馬爾多納多因為動力故障 ，成為了本站第二位退賽車手。第6圈，丹尼爾·科維亞特超過費利佩·馬薩來到第8名。羅曼·格羅斯讓在前幾圈也有極快的速度，他在第8圈超越另一位威廉斯車手鮑達斯，來到第6名。<ref name="guardrace" />
[[File:Bottas_in_spa_2015.JPG|left]]的車隊在他首次進站期間發生失誤，將他的車輛裝上3顆軟胎（黃色）及1顆中性胎（白色）。]]
里卡多在第8圈早早進站，接著，培瑞茲在隔圈進站，但墨西哥人出來後落在了紅牛之後。幾位車手也在接下來的幾圈內進站，其中包括鮑達斯及格羅斯讓，威廉斯車手在進站期間奪回他的名次，不過在第10圈再度被蓮花車手超回來。晚些，鮑達斯卻因為車隊為他同時換上兩種不同的輪胎配方，被判罰通過維修道一次。<ref name="guardrace2">{{cite web|last1 = McVeigh|first1 = Niall|title = F1: Lewis Hamilton wins the Belgian Grand Prix 2015 – as it happened|url = http://www.theguardian.com/sport/live/2015/aug/23/f1-belgian-grand-prix-live-2015|publisher = The Guardian|accessdate = 2015-08-23|date = 2015-08-23|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150826135824/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/live/2015/aug/23/f1-belgian-grand-prix-live-2015|archivedate = 2015-08-26|deadurl = no}}</ref>第11圈，馬克斯·維斯塔潘執行了一次冒險的超車，他在布蘭奇蒙特從外側超越納斯爾，來到第11名。<ref name="bbcrace" />經過這些進站後，前段的車手依次為漢米爾頓、羅斯堡、維泰爾、雷克南及里卡多，其中前四位車手仍未進站。在這四位車手中，羅斯堡於第13圈首先進站，出來後剛好落在前一圈超過里卡多的培瑞茲前頭。墨西哥人帶著他的氣勢從艾爾羅格彎一直到7號彎，不過最終無法從梅賽德斯手中奪回名次。漢米爾頓與維泰爾分別在第14及第15圈進站換胎。<ref name="guardrace2" />

在接下來的幾圈內，羅斯堡持續追擊前方的漢米爾頓，不過始終無法追近。第18圈，羅曼·格羅斯讓超越里卡多來到第4名。2圈後，他利用[[DRS|DRS]]從培瑞茲手中奪下第3名。第21圈，丹尼爾·里卡多的紅牛突然停在了巴士站（{{lang|en|Bus Stop}}）減速彎的邊上，迫使賽會出動虛擬安全車。許多車手選擇在此期間進佔換上新胎，其中包括格羅斯讓、馬薩和維斯塔潘。<ref name=bbcrace />到了第28圈，科維亞特進站換上新的軟胎，這套胎讓他能以較快的速度跑到比賽結束，另一方面，維泰爾則選擇不進站，嘗試使用舊有的輪胎跑到比賽結束。科維亞特的新胎令他超越鮑達斯、雷克南、馬薩及培瑞茲，最終以第4名完賽。第31圈，漢米爾頓執行他的第二次換胎，而隊友羅斯堡也在隔圈進站。小卡洛斯·塞恩斯最終在第34圈以退賽收場。羅斯堡寫下最快圈速，並將他與隊友的差距縮小至10秒。<ref name=guardrace />然而，維泰爾的策略並未奏效。到了第42圈，距離比賽結束僅剩2圈時，他的右後輪在凱莫（{{lang|fr|Kemmel}}）大直道上爆胎，將頒獎台名次拱手讓給了格羅斯讓。<ref name=vettel1>{{cite web|last1=Richards|first1=Giles|title=Ferrari’s Sebastian Vettel unhappy with Pirelli after tyre explosion|url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/aug/23/ferrari-sebastian-vettel-pirelli-tyre-explosion|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=2015-08-24|date=2015-08-23|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150824191808/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/aug/23/ferrari-sebastian-vettel-pirelli-tyre-explosion|archivedate=2015-08-24|deadurl=no}}</ref>德國人將車輛開回維修站結束他的比賽，不過他仍具有第12名的成績。最後一圈，馬克斯·維斯塔潘嘗試在大直道超越雷克南，不過最後輪胎鎖死未能成功。最終，路易斯·漢米爾頓並未受到來自隊友的壓力，奪下他的第39座分站冠軍。<ref name=guardrace />

=== 賽後 ===
[[File:Grosjean_third_in_Spa.JPG|thumb]]
在[[大衛·庫塔_(賽車手)|大衛·庫塔]]主持的頒獎台訪問中，路易斯·漢米爾頓表示他「跑在前頭還算輕鬆」，稱他在比賽中唯一要擔心的就是輪胎磨損。尼可·羅斯堡認為他的比賽「全被起跑搞砸」，補充說漢米爾頓「表現非常出色，故這場勝利事他應得的」。羅曼·格羅斯讓很高興他生涯第10度站上頒獎台，說道「這是一個令人難以置信的周末」，稱「感覺就像是贏了分站冠軍」。當被問及他將問鼎世界冠軍，漢米爾頓依然強調「現在談論這還太早」。在賽後的記者會上，格羅斯讓形容維泰爾爆胎的當下「有點嚇人」，表示他如此的遭遇「非常不走運」。<ref name="conf">{{cite web|title = Belgian GP: Post-race F1 press conference transcript|url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120452|website = autosport.com|accessdate = 2015-08-25|date = 2015-08-23|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150827011437/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120452|archivedate = 2015-08-27|deadurl = no}}</ref>[[File:Roberto_Merhi_Belgium_2015.jpg|left]]連續四站在隊友[[威爾·史蒂文斯|威爾·史蒂文斯]]前頭完賽。]]賽後，賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾嚴厲批評輪胎供應商倍耐力，表示不僅涉及到他，尼可·羅斯堡在週五也遭遇同樣的事情。他表示：「我認為這應當是件持續在討論的事情，但卻沒有人關注。無法容許這件事的發生。如果尼可說他沒有跑開，那麼他就是沒有，他為什麼需要騙我們呢？我的情況也是相同的，我沒有跑開賽道，輪胎就這樣突然破裂……」他認為車手置身在危險之中，聲稱「如果爆胎提前200公尺發生，我現在就不會站在這了。」<ref name="vettel2">{{cite web|title = F1: Sebastian Vettel attacks Pirelli after late tyre failure at Belgian Grand Prix|url = http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/aug/23/sebastian-vettel-attacks-pirelli-belgian-gp-failure|publisher = The Guardian|accessdate = 2015-08-24|date = 2015-08-23|language = en|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150824071302/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/aug/23/sebastian-vettel-attacks-pirelli-belgian-gp-failure|archivedate = 2015-08-24|deadurl = no}}</ref>倍耐力的賽車運動總監{{Le|保羅·亨伯利|Paul Hembery}}對維泰爾的指控做出回應：「我並不打算批評賽巴斯蒂安。這只是一時的火氣，且我不想在這個話題中加入戰局，這對每個人來說都毫無意義。當我們看到比賽剩餘的圈數，我們對此感到擔心。沒有人會認為他們將採用一停策略，在大家都在討論著該執行兩停或三停的情況下，這實在有點令人出乎意料。」<ref name="vettel22">{{cite web|title = F1: Sebastian Vettel attacks Pirelli after late tyre failure at Belgian Grand Prix|url = http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/aug/23/sebastian-vettel-attacks-pirelli-belgian-gp-failure|publisher = The Guardian|accessdate = 2015-08-24|date = 2015-08-23|language = en|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150824071302/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/aug/23/sebastian-vettel-attacks-pirelli-belgian-gp-failure|archivedate = 2015-08-24}}</ref>然而，尼可·羅斯堡選擇支持他的同胞維泰爾，他告訴記者：「遭遇爆胎相當的不幸。這本不該發生。這件事在其他的賽事不斷地出現，我在週五也遭遇到同樣的狀況。所幸我們兩人都沒出事。如果提早或再晚個幾公尺發生，我們就會遭受史上最大的翻車之一。他們必須尋求讓輪胎更安全的方法。」<ref name=vettel1 />考慮到即將到來的[[2015年義大利大獎賽|義大利大獎賽]]，他也呼籲官方能立即採取行動，因為[[國立蒙札賽車場|蒙札賽道]]是整年賽季中最快的賽道。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Collantine|first1=Keith|title=Rosberg wants action on tyres before Monza|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/23/rosberg-wants-action-on-tyres-before-monza/|publisher=F1Fanatic|accessdate=2015-08-24|date=2015-08-23|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828145543/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/23/rosberg-wants-action-on-tyres-before-monza/|archivedate=2015-08-28}}</ref>倍耐力則回應指出，他們早在{{F1|2013}}底便提出了設置一套胎的可跑圈數上限的建議。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Collantine|first1=Keith|title=Pirelli says drivers should be given maximum stint lengths for its tyres|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/23/pirelli-says-drivers-should-be-given-maximum-stint-lengths-for-its-tyres/|publisher=F1Fanatic|accessdate=2015-08-24|date=2015-08-23|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828150353/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/23/pirelli-says-drivers-should-be-given-maximum-stint-lengths-for-its-tyres/|archivedate=2015-08-28}}</ref>比賽過後一天，倍耐力宣布他們在其他車隊的輪胎上發現了裂痕，主要集中在後輪，且他們將會持續調查輪胎破損的原因。然而，該公司重申他們的立場指出，羅斯堡的爆胎起因於外力破壞，而維泰爾則「單純出於磨損」。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Noble|first1=Jonathan|title=Pirelli found more tyre cuts over Belgian GP weekend|url=http://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/pirelli-found-more-tyre-cuts-over-belgian-gp-weekend|website=motorsport.com|accessdate=2015-08-25|date=2015-08-24|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828151955/http://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/pirelli-found-more-tyre-cuts-over-belgian-gp-weekend|archivedate=2015-08-28}}</ref>維泰爾也獲得前一級方程式賽車車手大衛·庫塔及庫塔的前隊友米卡·海基寧的支持，<ref>{{cite web|title=Hakkinen 'understands' Vettel's anger|url=http://www.planetf1.com/driver/55667788/74703/Hakkinen-understands-Vettels-anger|website=planetf1.com|accessdate=2015-08-29|date=2015-08-29|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150902074353/http://www.planetf1.com/driver/55667788/74703/Hakkinen-understands-Vettels-anger|archivedate=2015-09-02}}</ref>庫塔更認為維泰爾跟倍耐力交涉這項輪胎議題相當正確。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Coulthard|first1=David|title=David Coulthard column: Vettel right to tackle Pirelli on tyres|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34043197|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2015-08-26|date=2015-08-24|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825013028/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34043197|archivedate=2015-08-25}}</ref>這位法拉利車手於週二再度捍衛車隊所決定的一停策略，表示：「我們從來都不會冒險決定策略，一點都不會。車隊不該被指責。」<ref>{{cite web|title=Sebastian Vettel defends Ferrari strategy after tyre blow-out during Belgian GP|url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/aug/26/sebastian-vettel-defends-ferrari-belgian-grand-prix|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=2015-08-26|date=2015-08-25|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828152835/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/aug/26/sebastian-vettel-defends-ferrari-belgian-grand-prix|archivedate=2015-08-28}}</ref>
[[File:Max_Verstappen_Belgium_2015.jpg|thumb]]對[[費利佩·納斯爾|費利佩·納斯爾]]的超車受到了讚揚。]]
馬克斯·維斯塔潘在布蘭奇蒙特對費利佩·納斯爾的超車特別受到好評。前一級方程式賽車車手{{le|艾倫·麥克尼什|Allan McNish}}寫道：「這是我一生當中，首次見到有人從布蘭奇蒙特地外側超越別人。這次的超車大受歡迎。」<ref name=bbcreport>{{cite web|last1=Benson|first1=Andrew|title=Lewis Hamilton eases to Belgian GP win ahead of Nico Rosberg|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34034314|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2015-08-24|date=2015-08-23|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828153536/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/34034314|archivedate=2015-08-28}}</ref>另外，在整場比賽遭遇電池電量不足的問題後，簡森·巴頓僅能在兩輛馬諾瑪魯西亞前頭完賽，稱麥拉倫的這場比賽是個「窘境」。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Esler|first1=William|title=Jenson Button brands McLaren's Belgian GP an 'embarrassment'|url=http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/24180/9962944/jenson-button-brands-mclarens-belgian-gp-an-embarrassment|publisher=Sky Sports|accessdate=2015-08-24|date=2015-08-24|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150824131741/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/24180/9962944/jenson-button-brands-mclarens-belgian-gp-an-embarrassment|archivedate=2015-08-24}}</ref>蓮花透露馬爾多納多的退賽一部份是起因於「與路緣石過度接觸」。技術總監尼克·切斯特（{{lang|en|Nick Chester}}） 認為這是「一個很大的憾事」，馬爾多納多在退賽前一直跑在最終取得季軍的格羅斯讓前頭，也因此無法為車隊貢獻一個好成績。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Collantine|first1=Keith|title=Kerbs contributed to Maldonado’s retirement|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/23/kerbs-contributed-to-maldonado-retirement/|publisher=F1Fanatic|accessdate=2015-08-24|date=2015-08-23|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828154638/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/23/kerbs-contributed-to-maldonado-retirement/|archivedate=2015-08-28}}</ref>蓮花隨後又透露這次的退賽是出於他在艾爾羅格跑開後，造成的離合器控制系統損壞。同時，車隊讚許格羅斯讓的駕駛「無可挑剔」。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Barretto|first1=Lawrence|last2=Anderson|first2=Ben|title=Pastor Maldonado's Belgian GP retirement was self-inflicted – Lotus|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120475|website=autosport.com|accessdate=2015-08-25|date=2015-08-24|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828155200/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120475|archivedate=2015-08-28}}</ref>賽車記者{{le|馬克·休斯 (記者)|Mark Hughes (journalist)|馬克·休斯}}也稱讚格羅斯讓在一級方程式賽車界「還是被過度低估」。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hughes|first1=Mark|title=Why Romain Grosjean is still seriously under-rated in F1|url=http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/32420/9965114/why-romain-grosjean-is-still-seriously-under-rated-in-f1|publisher=Sky Sports|accessdate=2015-08-26|date=2015-08-26|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828155450/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/32420/9965114/why-romain-grosjean-is-still-seriously-under-rated-in-f1|archivedate=2015-08-28}}</ref>威廉斯對維爾特利·鮑達斯在第一次進站的輪胎混搭事件展開內部調查，認為這讓鮑達斯損失了上頒獎台的機會。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Collantine|first1=Keith|title=Williams to investigate bizarre Bottas tyre mix-up|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/24/williams-to-investigate-bizarre-bottas-tyre-mix-up/|publisher=F1Fanatic|accessdate=2015-08-25|date=2015-08-24|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828155812/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2015/08/24/williams-to-investigate-bizarre-bottas-tyre-mix-up/|archivedate=2015-08-28}}</ref>

由於比賽的結果，路易斯·漢米爾頓將他與羅斯堡的積分差拉大至28分，這也是本季至今雙方最大的差距。維泰爾因為爆胎，使得他在積分榜上落後漢米爾頓67分。<ref>{{cite web|title=2015 Driver Standings|url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/results/2015-driver-standings.html|publisher=FIA|accessdate=2015-08-25|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828160405/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/results/2015-driver-standings.html|archivedate=2015-08-28}}</ref>在車隊積分榜方面，梅賽德斯與法拉利間的差距擴大至184分，而蓮花擠下了原先位居第五的印度威力，上升一個名次。<ref>{{cite web|title=2015 Constructor Standings|url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/results/2015-constructor-standings.html|publisher=FIA|accessdate=2015-08-25|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828160620/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/results/2015-constructor-standings.html|archivedate=2015-08-28}}</ref>
